    title: "Belangrijke informatie feestavond 2017!",
    description:
      '<p style="margin: 0px 0px 6px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1d2129; font-size: 14px;">Bezoekers van de feestavond opgelet!</p>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 6px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1d2129; font-size: 14px;"><br />Hieronder staat belangrijke informatie omtrent de feestavond op 11 februari a.s. in de&nbsp;<a class="profileLink" style="color: #365899; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; font-family: inherit;" href="https://www.facebook.com/brikkeoave/" data-hovercard="/ajax/hovercard/page.php?id=807684849299783" data-hovercard-prefer-more-content-show="1">Brikke Oave</a>.<br />- De deuren gaan om 19:00 uur open.<br />- Garderobe is verplicht.<br />- Consumptieprijs &euro;2,- (bonnen zijn alleen op 11 februari 2017 geldig).</p>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 6px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1d2129; font-size: 14px;"><span class="text_exposed_show" style="display: inline; font-family: inherit;">- Er kan NIET gepind worden.<br />- Verkleed komen is wel zo leuk!<br />- Aan de deur zijn GEEN entreekaarten meer te koop.</span></p>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 6px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1d2129; font-size: 14px;"><span class="text_exposed_show" style="display: inline; font-family: inherit;"><br /></span></p>\n<div class="text_exposed_show" style="display: inline; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1d2129; font-size: 14px;">\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 6px; font-family: inherit;">Tot zaterdag!</p>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 6px; font-family: inherit;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="margin: 6px 0px; font-family: inherit;">Alaaf !!</p>\n<p style="margin: 6px 0px; font-family: inherit;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="margin: 6px 0px; font-family: inherit;">&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n<p><img src="https://carnavalsradio.nl/image.axd?picture=2017%2f2%2f15972371_1331106240270175_8172903381293915735_o.jpg" alt="" /></p>',
